      <title>Cycle Pharmaceuticals 准备以 4.88 亿美元收购 Vanda</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/cycle-pharma-is-said-to-stand-by-488-million-offer-for-vanda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Vanda 的一种药物未能获得监管部门批准后，Cycle Pharmaceuticals Ltd. 仍然有意收购 Vanda Pharmaceuticals Inc.。]]></description>
